---
title: Carb Smart Wonton-Inspired Plant-Based Ground Protein Meatballs with Stir-Fried Veggies
description: This Chinese-inspired dish offers all the delicious flavours of dumplings, but without the wrapper. Minced green onion adds layers of juiciness to the plant-based ground protein mix, while fragrant ginger, zucchini, snap peas and mushrooms tie the dish together.
